trans-unit.source: Contains methods and properties that are used to manage queries to the tracking data that is contained in the SQL database used by a <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService" />.
trans-unit.target: 包含用于管理跟踪数据查询的方法和属性，跟踪数据包含在 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService" /> 使用的 SQL 数据库中。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery> provides methods and properties that you can use in order to access certain kinds of tracking data stored in a SQL database by the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery> 提供了一些方法和属性，您可以使用这些方法和属性来访问 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService> 存储在 SQL 数据库中的某些种类的跟踪数据。

trans-unit.source: Access to this data is provided through <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objects.
trans-unit.target: 对此数据的访问是通过 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> 对象提供的。

trans-unit.source: You can call <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.TryGetWorkflow%2A> to try to get a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> for a specific workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: 您可以调用 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.TryGetWorkflow%2A> 尝试获取特定工作流实例的 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>。

trans-unit.source: You can call <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A> to get a collection of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objects that correspond workflow instances that have tracking data that matches a set of query parameters contained in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions> that is passed as a parameter to the method.
trans-unit.target: 您可以调用 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A> 来获取 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> 对象的集合，这些对象对应于具有跟踪数据的工作流实例，该跟踪数据与包含在作为参数传递到方法的 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions> 中的一组查询参数匹配。

trans-unit.source: See the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> class for more information about the kind of tracking data available and see the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions> class for more information about the kind of queries that can be performed.
trans-unit.target: 有关可用跟踪数据种类的更多信息，请参见 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> 类，有关可执行的查询的种类的更多信息，请参见 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions> 类。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: The default constructor initializes <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.ConnectionString%2A> to a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: 默认构造函数会将 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.ConnectionString%2A> 初始化为一个空引用（在 Visual Basic 中为 `Nothing`）。

trans-unit.source: You must set <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.ConnectionString%2A> before you call <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.TryGetWorkflow%2A> or an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException> will be thrown.
trans-unit.target: 必须在调用 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.ConnectionString%2A> 或 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A> 之前设置 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.TryGetWorkflow%2A>，否则将引发 <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>。

trans-unit.source: The connection string of the SQL database to query.
trans-unit.target: 要查询的 SQL 数据库的连接字符串。
